reviews.text:
Overall environment is comfortable. we ordered the lunch sets. 

Rice quality is good. when we tried to order the rice but waitress said net rice order is unavailable. but after few minutes she gave us a bowl of rice for free. What a warm service!

Lamp chop isn't overcooked but it's rather salty. less salt or pepper is recommended.

Fried Salmon is well maintained. 

will probably try again next time!
Nice waitress and environment, easy access by mtr
Definitely recommend this place if you want a cozy place to grab a drink!! I will come more often with friends
Nice quiet place to hang out with friends, good atmosphere to talk and laugh. Good choices of cocktails and beers.

I tried the Freeflow in an envening with customer. This Freeflow is absolutely within my control of the expenses. And I have great time with my guests over the drinks in such an open and friendly atmosphere. But bar food is not in the Freeflow. 
Gathering with friends or customers here is great. The environment is comfortable and the music is good, location is in the conjunction of 3 rail lines that easily access from different parts of the city.

地點超方便，新裝修坐得舒服，服務好好～
Nice waitress and environment, easy access by mtr

中規中矩，午餐試唔到太多，味道唔差，又唔係收得特別貴，可以。
羊扒，保雲酥幾脆，加上黃芥末醬，肉唔係好多筋又唔係過老，$88有三件，可以。  伴碟冷冷的送上， 感覺一般。
三文魚，無乜特別，香煎了一下，飯也不是突出。

唯一係位置太大風，對流大強，門口位置吹得辛苦一點。
Definitely recommend this place if you want a cozy place to grab a drink!! I will come more often with friends
